## "But I have discovered, for over 15 years now, a world full of challenges and complexity, with learning just as interesting."

**Naval officer, expert then coach:** Marie Emmanuelle shares the issues linked to these two major career transitions in **La Baille**, the review of former students of the Naval Academy and associations of officers of the French Navy.

[**Article available in full here.**](https://all-leaders.fr/documents/25_Article-ME-dans-La-Baille.pdf)

{% Pdf url="/documents/25_Article-ME-dans-La-Baille.pdf" height="800px" /%}

